Invocation Name: my realtor
des:
Our voice app for real estate firms will be of great use, as it will provide their clients an additional channel. Since, no human intervention is required from the real estate firms' end, the answer that the client gets is almost instantaneous, hence resulting in enhanced customer experience.

Launch the skill and simply say "help" to know the available commands. 

This is a demo voice app developed by Digitall DNA. 
For development or integration related queries, please contact us via our website www.thedigitaldna.net
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
